title: 'Sparkle for captaincy': Ponting hails Iyer as PBKS clinch top-two finish

author: TOI LIFESTYLE DESK
description: Miley Cyrus revealed that her distinctive raspy voice is partly due to Reinke's edema, a vocal cord condition causing swelling. While she acknowledges it makes performing challenging, she credits the condition for contributing to her unique vocal tone and texture. Cyrus is hesitant about surgery, fearing it could alter her signature sound.
title: What is Reinke's edema, rare condition behind Miley Cyrus' iconic voice

author: SOUMITRA BOSE
description: Sunita, a 43-year-old woman from Nagpur, faces espionage charges after being handed over by Pakistani authorities. She crossed the LoC to meet Pakistani contacts, raising suspicions of spying due to heightened tensions. Authorities are scrutinizing her communications, investigating whether her actions were driven by personal relationships or a larger espionage plot, while her son is being escorted back to Nagpur.
title: Spy or lover? Nagpur woman's chats with Pakistan contacts raise questions

author: TOI NEWS DESK
description: External affairs minister Jaishankar asserted that India's military actions, not US mediation, compelled Pakistan to agree to a ceasefire. He criticized China's close defense ties with Pakistan and highlighted Pakistan's open support for terrorism. Jaishankar also addressed India's relationship with Russia, European double standards, and the progress of the India-EU Free Trade Agreement, expressing optimism about Indo-German defense cooperation.
title: ‘Draw your conclusions’: Jaishankar hints at China’s role in Pakistan conflict

author: TOI SPORTS DESK
description: Taylor Swift's Instagram activity has ignited a frenzy among fans, with some noticing a discrepancy in her post count, fueling speculation about a potential new album announcement. Meanwhile, Swift and Travis Kelce are reportedly distancing themselves from Blake Lively and Ryan Reynolds due to a disagreement involving Justin Baldoni. Sources suggest Swift is relieved to end the friendship.
title: Taylor Swift fans panic over cryptic Instagram post after Travis Kelce date

author: TOI ENTERTAINMENT DESK
description: Reports suggest that Deepika Padukone’s exit from Prabhas starrer Spirit stemmed from a series of disagreements with Sandeep Reddy Vanga. The Padmaavat actress had allegedly demanded over Rs 20 crore as remuneration, along with shorter working hours to accommodate her schedule as a new mother. According to reports, Triptii Dimri is being paid around Rs 4 crore for her role, significantly less than Deepika’s reported fee.
title: Triptii Dimri bags Vanga's Spirit for Rs 4 cr, far less than Deepika's fee: Report

author: TOI SPORTS DESK
description: Co-owner Preity Zinta's exuberant celebration stole the show as Punjab Kings secured a top-two finish in the IPL league stage. Skipper Shreyas Iyer's match-winning six against Mumbai Indians triggered Zinta's passionate outburst. The victory, fueled by Inglis and Arya's impressive partnership, gives Punjab Kings a crucial advantage in the playoffs.
title: Watch: Preity Zinta can't hold back emotions as Iyer seals Qualifier 1 spot
